天就要回国了，但是留下了非常美好的回忆。\n和大家道别以后，我应该也能一直保持笑容","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":328,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":328,"voiceId":"event208-03-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":328}],"windowDisplayName":"妮可莉娜","body":"呵呵，我有点羡慕\n总是在一起的你们呢","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":328,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":328,"voiceId":"event208-03-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"美咲","body":"总是……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"pui01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"event208-03-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":328}],"windowDisplayName":"妮可莉娜","body":"………………","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":328,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":328,"voiceId":"event208-03-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"美咲","body":"……妮可莉娜公主？\n怎么了吗？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15